Tie-RangeHash version 0.01
==========================

Tie::RangeHash creates a hash that takes numeric ranges as its keys.  You can then
reference the value assigned to the range using a member of that range.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

   none right now.

